snippet.title: Primal Survivors Gameplay Trailer | Steam PC
snippet.description:
Throw colossals bones and big rocks in an ever growing horde of primal creatures to survive in the jungle. Choose from a variety of upgrades to create unique and game-breaking builds. Unlock a diverse cast of classes and weapons with unique powers.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1492150/Primal_Survivors/

Features
◘ 50 skills sets represented with cards for a unique experience every run!
◘ 25 permanent upgrades
◘ 2 Classes and more to come
◘ 2 Weapons and more to come
◘ 10 minutes play session for busy gamers
